ygData.subject: Re: [EQ_women] I'm a new member
ygData.msgSnippet: Nice to meet you Sue.  I agree about the men.  and it s so hard to tell who is who in game as well.  I don t get a chance to post here or play eq as much as I
ygData.messageBody:
Nice to meet you Sue. I agree about the men. and
it's so hard to tell who is who in game as well. I
don't get a chance to post here or play eq as much as
I would like, but I like the comfortable feeling here.
I've been playing on the Povar server for a little
over 2 years. I have tiny toons on a few other
servers but I can't remember which ones atm. hehehe.
nice to meet you.

Ainthara

<P>I'm new to EQ women and love the fact that

trying to talk EQ talk with guys. Even in the game

<P>My name is Sue, I am 43 mother of 3
(grown&gone) kids and have been a gameaholic for
the better part of 25 years. </P>
<DIV></DIV>
<P>I have a lvl 38 Shaman Vah Shir - Nofreesowforu
</P>
<DIV></DIV>
<P>a lvl 6 Human Warrior - Diixii, and a lvl 9 Cleric
- Pletora. All on the Berrel Server. Oh and like
all of us I have a "mule" in the Bazaar. Send me a
tell and let the killing begin ')<BR></P>
